manhattan.waveformdata

クラス PartialID

  • java.lang.Object
    • manhattan.waveformdata.BasicID
      • manhattan.waveformdata.PartialID

  • public class PartialID
extends BasicID

    ID for a partial derivative

    This class is IMMUTABLE
    =Contents of information for one ID=
    Name of station
    Name of network
    Horizontal position of station (latitude longitude)
    Global CMT ID
    Component (ZRT)
    Period minimum and maximum
    Start time
    Number of points
    Sampling Hz
    If one is convoluted or observed, true
    Position of a waveform for the ID
    partial type
    Location of a perturbation point: latitude, longitude, radius

    One ID volume:#oneIDbyte:

    導入されたバージョン:
    2013/12/1
    バージョン:
    0.2
    作成者:
    kensuke
